node.text:
"The sky above the port was the color of a television, tuned to a dead channel"
If you know where these words are from, I think you'll like what comes next

𝘾𝙮𝙗𝙚𝙧𝙥𝙪𝙣𝙠 𝙇𝙖𝙣𝙙𝙨𝙘𝙖𝙥𝙚𝙨

I've always loved cyberpunk related art. I grew up reading science fiction and cyberpunk novels, not to talk about movies, and I try to put that flavor in music.

Anyone wants to listen to some dystopian/apocalyptic/cyberpunk/science fiction related music?
Hope you enjoy 𝘾𝙮𝙗𝙚𝙧𝙥𝙪𝙣𝙠 𝙇𝙖𝙣𝙙𝙨𝙘𝙖𝙥𝙚𝙨
